{"tid":748293,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"香港府擬以打黑道法律封殺港獨政黨   英國議會要求英國政府向聯合國呼籲  香港法治及基本自由正遭受侵蝕","createTime":"2018-07-19T06:03:44.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-19T07:57:11.000Z","uid":35790,"like":18,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"9879f51cf779fcb408e9bd24e3803722446b84a3","tid":748293,"uid":35790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-19T06:03:44.000Z","msg":"港府擬以打黑道法律封殺港獨政黨 英國表關切<br />\n<br />\n〔即時新聞／綜合報導〕香港在1997年主權移交中國後，港府昨（17）日首次引用《社團條例》第八條，以「維護國家安全」為由，取締「主張港獨」的香港民族黨。此舉引來英國關切。<br />\n<br />\n綜合媒體報導，香港雖擁有中國所沒有的高度自治和言論、結社自由，但越來越受到日益崛起的中國所威脅。香港民族黨昨日隨即收到港府文件，內容援引《社團條例》第8條，以國家安全和公共秩序等考量，要求民族黨召集人陳浩天在21天內說明個人言行和政黨所為，並將以此決定是否禁止民族黨運作。該款條例最初被用來治理香港黑社會組織犯罪。<br />\n<br />\n港府認為民族黨的活動，可能威脅國家安全和公共安全，有意禁止；保安局局長李家超也表示，香港雖有結社自由的權利，但並非沒有限制。李家超並援引香港法律，表示「國安」意指捍衛「中華人民共和國的領土完整以及獨立」。<br />\n<br />\n對此，陳浩天認為，已成立2年的民主黨，現在突然被找麻煩的原因，推測是與自己近日訪問台灣有關；未來將會有更多的政治組織，受到該款條例的限制，呼籲全世界「最好密<br />\n切關注」。<br />\n<br />\n港府此舉也引來英國關切，英國外交部發表聲明表示，已關注到港府打算禁止香港民族黨繼續運作，英國雖不支持港獨，但香港享有高度自治、參選、言論和結社自由等權利，且均明定於香港「基本法」及香港人權法案。英國議會也於上週簽署一份信函，要求英國政府向聯合國呼籲，香港法治及基本自由正遭受侵蝕。<br />\n<a href=\"http://news.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/2492315\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F2492315&d=ffeL2UZe1D0zqWnfAH%2BT1Wi1w7%2FDyS2Kz%2BsYtkalU0Y%3D&h=d3f21a51\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F2492315&h=d398c243\" target=\"_blank\">http://news.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/2492315</a>"},{"pid":"07c1b127e8176a79ae580fcf02dde2cd5d154b90","tid":748293,"uid":35790,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-19T06:14:48.000Z","msg":"蜚聲國際"},{"pid":"fc396979b134f875ee7c68b835948b4c9c09c64e","tid":748293,"uid":176366,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-19T06:16:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"60a0319a73bd52dbfb9d7bca4da922bb5ad3af06","tid":748293,"uid":29270,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-19T06:18:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"16e7978922440241eb87df08c5530de6ab07be78","tid":748293,"uid":35790,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-19T06:19:38.000Z","msg":"1997年臨立會惡法"},{"pid":"2001e85e33c5ef761f20d6b08d905a984dbd016e","tid":748293,"uid":47359,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-19T06:20:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 大家唔好放棄"},{"pid":"41d7995df8618c0476f1af89351af7fe2ddabe2c","tid":748293,"uid":67500,"like":2,"dislike":6,"score":-4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-19T07:00:49.000Z","msg":"係幫手就97個時幫啦，出賣香港死英狗"},{"pid":"ee6b8945b5e92bb770615e4ea3d6355aea2ce45b","tid":748293,"uid":153689,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-19T07:03:27.000Z","msg":"香港殖民政府又再揚威國際<br />\n中國或成最大贏家<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"20b4c09b7679f0c338ea259fe23a251337afc725","tid":748293,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-19T07:04:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"09ea91766d39ffe868b39e3fb2a22bebbc1f15d9","tid":748293,"uid":30169,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-19T07:45:07.000Z","msg":"仲有法治咩？"},{"pid":"184617329175da35d2eee3560d36e3f8518b4da3","tid":748293,"uid":49588,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-19T07:54:28.000Z","msg":"香港還有法治嗎？"},{"pid":"034526691547daea3091301bd1d5936cb670dd23","tid":748293,"uid":68728,"like":0,"